public class PSORequiredFieldsItemValidation
extends PSOAbstractItemValidationExit
implements com.percussion.extension.IPSItemValidator

An item validation exit that checks for required fields. There are 2 required parameters:

  • The required fields.
  • Destination workflow states.
Both of these parameters are comma separated lists of values. If the item is transitioning into one of the listed states, then the required fields will be checked.

Note that some field types (particularly rich text fields) may appear to be blank when they actually contain data. This extension will treat these fields as if they are not empty.

Author:
DavidBenua
